The fake news locator bot addresses the story of Trey Gowdy's arrest in this folder . 

TreyGowdy custody.ipynb is the algorithm which aggregates fake news incidents state wise all over US and tweets out  which states in US has highest fake news activities. Also it tweets alert to journalists from specific states with highest fake news activity. 

Combined.csv is the main csv file consisting of tweets related to the incident of " Trey Gowdy in custody" from 22nd April 2017 to 06th 
May 2017.

geocoder.ipynb is the algorithm used for Geo coding location

normalized code2.csv is the dataset consisting of state wise aggregated tweets, Geo-coded location,State specific population,normalized activity rate of every state, journalists from those states, their twitter handle and news organization name.
